description: KHOMO introduces it first super extra long USB SYNC Charger for Asus Eee Pad Transformer Tablets. Does your existing cable not reach your nightstand in a hotel room? Tired of the short standard cord? Finally, a solution! With our 6 foot cable there will be no more leaning close to your outlet to use your tablet. It is convenient, easy to use, and 100% compatible with the existing Transformer Tablets. With high-quality rubberized A+ materials and sturdy engineering, this cable is a must have for in your home, car, traveling, and more.
title: KHOMO Pack of 2pcs Super Long 6ft (SIX Feet!) USB Data Charging Cable for Asus Eee Pad Transformer Prime TF101 TF201 TF300 TF700 SL101 TF303 (High Quality Rubberized Cable, not cheap Plastic)
